{"tid":993636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［理大民主牆］關同學否認所有控罪並拒絕道歉","createTime":"2019-01-24T05:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T03:08:42.000Z","uid":47359,"like":65,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5f495299bd64eefb40fc87423a793a030943b5","tid":993636,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"[關同學否認所有控罪並拒絕道歉］<br />\n一月廿三日理大紀律委員會（SDC)就著去年十月民主牆風波展開聆訊。<br />\nSDC委員忽視民主牆及言論自由之重要，全場言論帶有偏見謂：「關同學你而家爆粗噉第時做護士會唔會對病人爆粗？」；未審先判指控關同學講粗口係唔啱，有辱校譽（detrimental to reputation of university)。<br />\n關同學反指學校管理層先係侮辱校譽，自己企出嚟抗爭係想拯救校譽。而SDC不能單一睇爆粗就定性成件事。義有分大小，學校高層以至物業管理處（FMO）濫用公權力打壓民主牆更為可恥。<br />\n聆訊將近完結時SDC無恥地詢問關同學會否向FMO、當時在場嘅沈教授、莫教授道歉，關同學斷然拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudents.independence.union%2F&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=5c16540a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.independence.union%2F&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=c914d709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/</a>"},{"pid":"ee618b269762a3f72b969bf4d5f0c0b825acefbe","tid":993636,"uid":47359,"like":58,"dislike":5,"score":53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"你老味我好似去咗中學訓導處噉<br />\n成班prof話我唔應該講粗口<br />\n就算學校打壓言論自由，總有較好表達方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"df3b2cabeb7c85efb3e42b534d981f625c8d26aa","tid":993636,"uid":106426,"like":45,"dislike":11,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e5954fbbe4c5bc5b09263979d2eb12f9694ff32","tid":993636,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ee618b269762a